children but it is extended in case the other 3 children are girls.Completed application forms along with other documents must be submitted to the concerned authorities within 1 year of delivery.All those registered labourers whose wife is already taking maternity benefits from any board / dept. / corporation are not eligible.3. Eligibility Criteria for Haryana Labour Welfare Board Paternity Benefit SchemeAll the candidates must fulfill the eligibility criteria as mentioned in the table below to avail the Haryana Labour Board Paternity Benefit Scheme:-Eligibility CriteriaMembership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u0937at-least 1 yearApply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093eupto 5Scheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090fMaleContinue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940NoThe total assistance under paternity benefit scheme of Haryana labour is Rs. 21,000.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: hrylabour.gov.in  at  "}